<body>

  <div class="banner bg-image" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://static1.srcdn.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unforgiven-clint-eastwood-and-morgan-freeman-cropped-1.jpg);">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><strong>“Every time I go to a movie, it’s magic, no matter what the movie’s about.”</strong>!</h1>
      <p><em>-Steven Spielberg</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="d-flex row justify-content-center text-align">
